---
import "../styles/default.scss";
import "../styles/about-us.scss";
import og from "../images/og-image.png";
import Header from '../components/Header.jsx';
import Footer from '../components/footer.jsx';
const email_current="quirozben24@icloud.com";
const phone_current="425-610-5085";
---
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<title>About Us</title>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="title" content="About Us">
		<meta name="description" content="Gutter installation and repair services in Seattle and surrounding area. 
		Call us at (425) 610-5085 or email us to schedule a service today. We offer a variety of services.">
		<meta property="og:title" content="About Us">
		<meta property="og:type" content="website">
		<link rel="sitemap" href="/sitemap-index.xml">
		<meta property="og:image" content='https://bwgutter.com/og-image.png'/>
		<meta property="site_name" content="About Us">
		<meta name="theme-color" content="#4F4A3B">
		<style>
		@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:ital,wght@0,500;0,700;0,900;1,700&display=swap');
		</style>
		</head>
	<body>
	<header>
	<Header email={email_current} phone={phone_current} client:load/>
	</header>
    <div id='container'>
    <h1 id='title'>About Us</h1>
    <div id='about-us-text'>
        At BW Gutter Installation Services, we understand the vital role that gutters play in protecting your property from water damage. Whether it's heavy rain, melting snow, or any other form of precipitation, a well-maintained gutter system is crucial for directing water away from your roof, walls, and foundation. Our mission is to help you safeguard your investment and maintain a dry and structurally sound property.
        <br><br>What sets us apart is our dedication to excellence in every aspect of our work. We combine our expertise with the latest industry techniques and top-of-the-line equipment to provide efficient and effective gutter services. From installation and repairs to cleaning and maintenance, we handle all your gutter needs with utmost professionalism and attention to detail.
        <br><br>Customer satisfaction is our top priority, and we strive to exceed your expectations at every interaction. Our friendly and knowledgeable team is always ready to listen to your concerns, answer your questions, and provide expert advice tailored to your specific requirements. We believe in building long-term relationships with our clients, based on trust, reliability, and exceptional service.
    </div>
</div>
	<footer>
		<Footer/>
	</footer>
	</body>
</html>
